          "type": "text",
          "text": "3. Input Parameters"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The function likely takes one or more input parameters that represent attributes of a capital expenditure. These parameters could include:"
        }
